Package com.aston.group.stationdefender.gamesetting.items

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Item
    Item class represents an in-game item that the player can pick up, buy for credits, and use
    ItemBandages
    ItemBandages represents a bandage Item that can be used within the game
    ItemBlank
    ItemBlank represents a Blank Item with an ID of '0' and a name of 'Unknown Item'
    ItemBricks
    ItemBandages represents a brick Item that can be used within the game
    ItemBricksBlockade
    ItemBandages represents a blockage formed of bricks that can be used within the game
    ItemCement
    ItemBandages represents a cement Item that can be used within the game
    ItemCloseCombatWeapon
    ItemBandages represents a CloseCombatWeapon Item that can be used within the game
    ItemCredit
    ItemCredit is the in-game currency used.
    ItemHealth
    ItemBandages represents a health Item that can be used within the game to give the Tower additional health
    ItemMine
    ItemBandages represents a Mine Item that can be used within the game
    ItemStack<T extends Item>
    This class allows the Items to be stacked into a QuickSlot Inventory
    ItemTurret
    ItemBandages represents a Turret Weapon Item that can be used within the game
    ItemWater
    ItemBandages represents water that can be used within the game
    ItemWoodenBlockade
    ItemBandages represents a blockade formed of wood blocks that can be used within the game
    ItemWoodenBlocks
    ItemBandages represents a wooden block Item that can be used within the game
